      "description": "Simulated pump head (ΔP) versus flow rate curves were compared against experimental measurements at four rotational speeds. Mean absolute error across all operating points was 4.3%, well within the 10% acceptance threshold. These results provide confidence in the hydrodynamic fidelity of the CFD model prior to hemolysis prediction.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/pressure-rise-experimental-comparison",
      "meetsAcceptanceCriteria": true
    }
  ],
