    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 was confirmed across all candidate worst-case operating points. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The package is accepted for regulatory submission.",
